text:
🛖As you hike further in after the Park's entrance shelter to begin your journey, you come to a directional sign post and a Pond.
🐢🌿🍃This is the pond that greets you at the start of your hike.
Stop by to watch the sun-bathing terrapins.
🐢🐢🐢The tranquil Freshwater Pond is teeming with terrapins.
🐟🪰🐝Freshwater pond provides a conducive environment where aquatic life and other wildlife thrive, bringing about biodiversity to the freshwater habitat.
